  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ff881346bd87592829626151f10fafa7.poster.avif?t=1669991739\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ff881346bd87592829626151f10fafa7.webm?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ff881346bd87592829626151f10fafa7.mp4?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game follows a <strong>chinchilla</strong>, who awakens in a surreal world with a mysterious voice that looms over him. You have <strong>9 hours</strong> to defeat Darkness that threatens the earth.<br><br>The title’s gameplay and mechanics constitute a departure from the old <strong>3D platformer</strong> games, featuring a <strong>puzzle-like</strong> feeling to it, a <strong>detailed character movement</strong> and <strong>interesting visuals</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic Joystick Game Play.<br></li><li>21 Levels with individual Challenges.<br></li><li>Ranking with Steam Leaderboards.<br></li><li>Inclusion of Real-Time.<br></li><li>Punishing Mechanics.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ae68bc7aef4d359b0dc318e91bc9770f.poster.avif?t=1669991739\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ae68bc7aef4d359b0dc318e91bc9770f.webm?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ae68bc7aef4d359b0dc318e91bc9770f.mp4?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you up for the challenge?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ff881346bd87592829626151f10fafa7.poster.avif?t=1669991739\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ff881346bd87592829626151f10fafa7.webm?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ff881346bd87592829626151f10fafa7.mp4?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game follows a <strong>chinchilla</strong>, who awakens in a surreal world with a mysterious voice that looms over him. You have <strong>9 hours</strong> to defeat Darkness that threatens the earth.<br><br>The title’s gameplay and mechanics constitute a departure from the old <strong>3D platformer</strong> games, featuring a <strong>puzzle-like</strong> feeling to it, a <strong>detailed character movement</strong> and <strong>interesting visuals</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic Joystick Game Play.<br></li><li>21 Levels with individual Challenges.<br></li><li>Ranking with Steam Leaderboards.<br></li><li>Inclusion of Real-Time.<br></li><li>Punishing Mechanics.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ae68bc7aef4d359b0dc318e91bc9770f.poster.avif?t=1669991739\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ae68bc7aef4d359b0dc318e91bc9770f.webm?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1193790/extras/ae68bc7aef4d359b0dc318e91bc9770f.mp4?t=1669991739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br